italian consum price rise 0.4 pct in march itali 's consum price index rose 0.4 pct in march compar with februari after an ident increas in februari over januari , the nation statist institut istat said . the year-on-year rise in march wa 4.2 pct , unchang on februari and compar with 7.2 pct in march 1986. istat said it consum price index for the famili of worker and employe , base year 1985 equal 100 , regist 109.5 in march 1987 compar with 109.1 in februari thi year and 105.1 in march 1986 .